reviewText:
This is such a good book/study
So foundational and faith bolstering
Blew all the other Bible studies I've done out of the water

I have never highlighted more in any book and I am an avid reader so I was very excited to get these DVDs and do with a small group.  The material is fantastic and it has been a blessing to our group of small women.  Like drinking from a water fountain after wandering in the desert.
Had to stop in the middle of her talk for each lesson. Choppy presentation because of that
